markets.name: 1st Half - 1X2
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the final outcome of the 1st half of the match, either the win of the home team (1), a draw (X) or the win for the away team (2).

markets.name: 1st Half - Double Chance
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the outcome of the first half of the match. There are 3 possible outcomes: 1X (home team wins or draws at 1st half), X2 (away team wins or draws at 1st half), 12 (home team wins or the away team wins at 1st half).

markets.name: 1st Half - Total Goals
markets.oddsDescription: Predict whether the number of goals scored in first half of a match will be under/over the value specified.

markets.name: Multigoal HT
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the total number of goals that will be scored in 1st half of the match by choosing one of the available selections.

markets.name: 1st Half - Total Goals 1
markets.oddsDescription: You have to predict the total number of goals that will be scored during the first half by choosing one of the options.

markets.name: Chance Mix +
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the outcome of a halftime betting on two related bet types. If at least one selection is correct, the bet is winning. In case both selections are correct, the winnings won't be doubled.

markets.name: Home To Win Either Half
markets.oddsDescription: Predict whether home team will win atleast one half of the match.

markets.name: Away To Win Either Half
markets.oddsDescription: Predict whether away team will win atleast one half of the match.

markets.name: 1st Half - Correct Score
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the actual scoreline of the 1st half.

markets.name: HT/FT
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the outcome of the first half and the final outcome of the match. A halftime/full time bet is considered a winning only if both predictions of the halftime and full time are correct.

markets.name: 1st Half - Handicap 0.5
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the first half outcome of a match after the indicated handicap score has been applied to the half time result .For example, handicap score (0:2) indicates that the away team was given two goals advantage, handicap score (0.5:0) indicates that home team was given 0.5 goals advantage, etc. Asian handicap is two-way handicap, meaning that there are only 2 possible outcomes - win of the home team (1H) or win of the away team (2H). In the case of a whole goal handicap (value in brackets ends with ''1" or "4''), if the result is level after the handicap is taken into consideration, then all bets are void and stake refunded. By placing bet on value in brackets that represents quarter of one or more goals (value in brackets ends with ''0.5'' or ''1.5''), the bet can be half won (half of the stake multiplied by the odds is won) or half lost (half of the stake will be refunded).

markets.name: 1st Half - Draw No Bet
markets.oddsDescription: Predict which team will win 1st half of a match.Betsplaced on this market will be void if 1st half ends in adraw.

markets.name: 1st Half - Both Teams to Score
markets.oddsDescription: Predict if the two teams will score at least one goal each during 1st half of the match. The bet offers two possible outcomes: GG (both teams will score at least one goal during the 1st half); NG (one or none of the two teams will score at least one goal during the 1st half).

markets.name: 1st Half - Odd/Even Goals
markets.oddsDescription: Select whether the total number of goals scored in 1st half of a  match will be odd or even. Any 1st half of a match resulting in 0-0 will be settled on an even number of goals.

markets.name: 1st Half - 1X2 & Total Goals 1.5
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the final outcome of the 1st half, either the win of the home team (1), a draw (X) or the win for the guests (2) and predict whether the number of goals scored during the 1st half will be under/over the number specified.

markets.name: 1st Half - 1X2 & BTTS

markets.name: HT DC & GG/NG

markets.name: 1st Half - Double Chance & Total Goals 1.5
markets.oddsDescription: Predict the combination of 2 possible outcomes of the 1st half and number of goals scored during the 1st half offered.The bet is considered winning only if the outcome of bets for both combinations (markets) is correctly guessed.
